                    </div>
                    <span>This book is one of the best I have read on its subject. One of the things I liked best is that after reading the opening chapters, I could go to the two chapters that describe the time and space management styles that are unique to me. The tips found there are very helpful!<P>I recommend this book to all busy administrators who want to get a better handle on their time and space management skills. It's a quick read, and will easily pay for itself through the time and money saved. Great buy!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Awesome</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
